data.description: Amazing opportunity to purchase this gorgeous  2 story home, five bedrooms w/3.5 bathrooms-Master bedroom is downstairs- Open Kitchen /floor plan- separate laundry room downstairs four huge bedrooms upstairs with 2 full bathrooms w/walk-in closets and a huge game room recent carpet,  stove/microwave new, within last 4 years, generator for solar panels-newly renovated jack & jill bathroom-some wood blinds. Two HVAC units were replaced, one in January 2023 and one in December 2023. Foundation work was completed last week  Price reflects the need for minimal cosmetic work. The home is being sold "AS IS" The Owner will not do any repairs. Relax in the Oasis of a backyard along the green belt with an inground pool and awesome decking.
